CSVBaselStadt2TXT(List<String[]>) - Constructor for class de.ryanthara.ja.rycon.converter.text.CSVBaselStadt2TXT
Class constructor for read line based CSV files from the geodata server Basel Stadt (Switzerland).
CSVBaselStadt2Zeiss - Class in de.ryanthara.ja.rycon.converter.zeiss
This class provides functions to convert coordinate files from the geodata server Basel Stadt (Switzerland) into Zeiss REC files with it's dialects (R4, R5, REC500 and M5).
CSVBaselStadt2Zeiss(List<String[]>) - Constructor for class de.ryanthara.ja.rycon.converter.zeiss.CSVBaselStadt2Zeiss
Class constructor for read line based CSV files from the geodata server Basel Stadt (Switzerland).
